headline: CoStar Group Founder and CEO Andy Florance Named Among Top Ten on SP 200 List
summary: WASHINGTON, January 08, 2025--Andy Florance, Founder and Chief Executive Officer of CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP)("CoStar Group," "we" or "our"), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information and analytics in the property markets, today was named as one of the nation’s top ten most powerful executives in the residential real estate industry by Swanepoel Power 200 ("SP 200").
